{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/mercedes-benz-bosch-automated-ride-hailing-service/","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"f76d8f44-3bfb-5cae-94ff-67740138f7f5","html":"<p>After Hyundai Motor launched a so-called “BotRide” robotaxi test in Irvine, California, Mercedes-Benz and Bosch pilot their own Ride-hailing program in San José. This is the result of both companies working together for more than two years on solving issues related to operating autonomous vehicles safely on crowded city streets. </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The common goal is an SAE Level 4/5 driving system for fully automated and driverless vehicles, including the software for vehicle management.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/507e6/freeway.webp 200w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/28a80/freeway.webp 400w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/8d2ea/freeway.webp 800w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/68fc1/freeway.webp 1200w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/43d96/freeway.webp 1600w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/f5300/freeway.webp 5541w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/37402/freeway.jpg 200w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/4cda9/freeway.jpg 400w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/c60e9/freeway.jpg 800w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/6c738/freeway.jpg 1200w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/56dca/freeway.jpg 1600w,\n/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/737b3/freeway.jpg 5541w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/340986feb4bfdf7d183ed51561de7d38/c60e9/freeway.jpg\"\n          alt=\"&quot;Mercedes-Benz S-Class automated vehicle Ride-hailing service&quot;\"\n          title=\"Mercedes-Benz S-Class automated vehicle from the Ride-hailing service pilot program. More in thumbnail video\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Mercedes-Benz S-Class automated vehicle from the Ride-hailing service pilot program. More in thumbnail video</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>While Mercedes-Benz provides the vehicles, Bosch develops and manufactures components for urban automated driving. Participants hail a ride using an app developed by Daimler Mobility AG which allows potential ride-hailing partners to seamlessly integrate self-driving vehicles into their daily routine.</p>\n<p>\n      <div\n      class=\"gatsby-video-aspect-ratio\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; padding-top: 56.333333333333336%;\"\n      >\n    <video autoplay preload=\"auto\" loop playsinline muted style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: auto;\" >\n      <source src=\"/static/sensing-7d9e2a8f9ca056e76f4f3cb9b33be184-bb50b.webm\" type=\"video/webm\"><source src=\"/static/sensing-7d9e2a8f9ca056e76f4f3cb9b33be184-587b3.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    </video>\n    </div>\n    </p>\n<figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">The developed platform manages both self-driving and conventional vehicles, including operation and maintenance.</figcaption>\n<p>Read more about the platform and their pilot service from <a href=\"https://www.daimler.com/innovation/case/autonomous/pilot-city-san-jose.html\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Dailmer</a> and <a href=\"https://www.bosch-presse.de/pressportal/de/en/bosch-and-mercedes-benz-start-san-jose-pilot-project-for-automated-ridesharing-service-204032.html\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Bosch</a> media outlets.</p>\n<hr>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"After Hyundai Motor launched a so-called “BotRide” robotaxi test in Irvine, California, Mercedes-Benz and Bosch pilot their own Ride-hailing program in San José. This is the result of both companies working together for more than two years on solving issues related to operating autonomous vehicles safely on crowded city streets. "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"blockquote","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The common goal is an SAE Level 4/5 driving system for fully automated and driverless vehicles, including the software for vehicle management."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tagName":"figure","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-figure"],"style":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"],"style":"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-background-image"],"style":"padding-bottom: 65.49999999999999%; position: rela